Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Collins.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Collins (1994), 71 Ohio St.3d 310.]

(No. 94-2308 Submitted December 7, 1994 Decided December 23, 1994.) *311Geoffrey Stem, Disciplinary Counsel, and Alvin E. Mathews, Assistant Disciplinary Counsel, for relator. Baker, Chapman & Gaboon and Peter T. Cahoon, for respondent. Per Curiam.

We concur with the findings and recommendation of the board. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded and ordered to make restitution. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
